    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[bash fail then continue, fail then exit]]></title>
        <id>https://www.thiswind.work/post/bash-fail-then-continue-fail-then-exit/</id>
        <link href="https://www.thiswind.work/post/bash-fail-then-continue-fail-then-exit/">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-11-19T09:32:40.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>fail then continue</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"># process list of formulas that have been installed
while read i ;  do

    # Jump blank lines
    test -z &quot;$i&quot; &amp;&amp; continue

    echo &quot;Installing $i ...&quot;

    # attempt to install formula; if error write error, process next formula

    brew install &quot;$i&quot; || continue

done
</code></pre>
<p>fail then exit</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">some_command || exit
</code></pre>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>fail then continue</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"># process list of formulas that have been installed
while read i ;  do

    # Jump blank lines
    test -z &quot;$i&quot; &amp;&amp; continue

    echo &quot;Installing $i ...&quot;

    # attempt to install formula; if error write error, process next formula

    brew install &quot;$i&quot; || continue

done
</code></pre>
<p>fail then exit</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">some_command || exit
</code></pre>
]]></content>
